snippet.title: Automobilista 2 - Formula HiTech Gen2 @ Interlagos 1993 Gameplay
snippet.description:
AMS2 Gameplay as of the upcoming V1.5.3 update demonstrating recent AI development & featuring the new F-Hitech Gen2 cars @ Interlagos 1993, part of the new Historical Track Pack.  

Further details on the AMS2 November 2023 Dev Update here: https://forum.reizastudios.com/threads/automobilista-2-november-2023-development-update.32206/
